@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hcmcmw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.68) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.37)) + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.46) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.01)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.96) / (v1 + 0.72 * tmp + 0.75)) + (0.51 - 0.80))
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.51 / v1 + 0.61)) - v2)
    data[tid] = v0
